com.foreach.across.core.support

Class AttributeSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.core.support.AttributeSupport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReadableAttributes, WritableAttributes, org.springframework.core.AttributeAccessor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AttributeOverridingSupport

    public abstract class AttributeSupport
extends Object
implements WritableAttributes
    Support class for WritableAttributes, providing a base implementation of all methods. To be extended by subclasses. See AttributeOverridingSupport for a base implementation that supports overriding attributes from a parent.
    See Also:
    AttributeOverridingSupport
